{"tid":2354302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【證據喺度呀你老味！】乜撚野攬鈔巴？捉完前線鬼，就捉國際線鬼，捉撚完未姐？ 2","createTime":"2021-01-05T11:17:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T15:24:38.000Z","uid":379267,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"802ed3e7eb75c1c3b6e13e85b598cf798a66e834","tid":2354302,"uid":379267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T11:17:12.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"small\">【證據喺度呀你老味！】乜撚野攬鈔巴？捉完前線鬼，就捉國際線鬼，捉撚完未姐？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"large\">忍足幾個月，日日夜夜喺度單單打打，含血噴人。屈受襲重傷係假、眾籌幾千萬印印腳、攬鈔鈀乜乜柒柒</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"orange\">證據喺度呀你老味！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CctcYmGXJ4M\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCctcYmGXJ4M&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=89170193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CctcYmGXJ4M</a><br />\n(Back-up: <a href=\"https://vimeo.com/496736719\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F496736719&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAGzcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=b60650a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/496736719</a>)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一直無公開，原因一黎血腥，二黎當時身分未曝光，三黎真係<strong><span class=\"red\">估唔到香港人可以癲L到，捉鬼捉到無所不用其極。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n立場、蘋果、外媒全部都睇過証據，verified先報導！依段片，就係有腎上腺素頂住嗰陣為通知teammates而錄低。<br />\n<br />\n有無報警？有。<br />\n有無入院？有，醫院手帶、入院紙、腦震盪醫生紙都有！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">點解有暗花都一個人出街？咁係咪要一世留喺屋企？爛命一條，請乜保鏢？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"x-large\">仲有，成L日話我籌幾千萬嘆世界。</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">嘆你老味！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n日日返完工、進修之外，就係放晒時間喺光復香港。<strong><span class=\"red\">仆心仆命，仆到家庭破碎，仆到返唔到香港，仆到全球通緝，仆到一無所有！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">錢？</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"large\">一個崩都無袋過之餘，啲支出仲係自己倒貼。<span class=\"red\">重光團隊同人食飯會claim 錢，但係我兩袖清風從來無claim任何野</span>，一個崩都無呀！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n重光團隊自己都承認全面控制1,600萬，佢地要hold錢、要推BNO，攬炒團隊同我10月已經無奈接受，由佢地。無資源就馬死落地行。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">但點L解唔問真正hold錢嘅重光做緊乜，走去屈鳩我有幾千萬洗？</span></span></strong>更何況，我地無每個月燒幾十萬落lobbying firms推BNO。<br />\n<br />\n螞蟻暫緩一役，我<strong><span class=\"red\">講L咗好多次係中共內鬥造成。</span></strong><strong><span class=\"orange\">攬炒團隊同我係呼籲大家行動，封埋最後一口釘，迫佢直情取消，而唔係暫緩就算。</span></strong><strong>唔L係take credit！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>家長？</strong><strong><span class=\"red\">無</span></strong><br />\n<strong>金主？</strong><strong><span class=\"red\">無</span></strong><br />\n<strong>Patreon？</strong><strong><span class=\"red\">無</span></strong><br />\n<strong>Payme？</strong><strong><span class=\"red\">無</span></strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">乜柒都無，犧牲成個人生幫香港就有！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\">搞全球集會遊行、登報、寫論述、投稿、安排議員訪港，打Twitter，乜柒都做，乜柒都去盡力試，足足堅持咗一年半都無放棄過。</span><br />\n</strong><br />\n結果呢？<br />\n拉又拉過。<br />\n傷又傷過。<br />\n通緝又通緝緊。<br />\n洗頭艇又隨時坐。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"red\">同暴動手足一樣犧牲晒所有。結果，就係俾人日日單單打打，捉鬼，得寸進尺。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n到底前世係咪欠撚咗香港？同你交換人生好唔好？其他流亡手足會唔會墮落我唔知，我就一L定唔會！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">之前捉前線鬼，而家就捉國際線鬼，捉撚夠未姐？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"8fd9097ff62eeef732190e0ca96f5299f9d1a9e8","tid":2354302,"uid":278783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T15:24:38.000Z","msg":"唉"}]}